-- Kingfisher Air Seeks Two-Year Freeze on Loan Repayment, Express Reports
-- Thomas Abraham
-- 2010-07-28T01:20:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-28/kingfisher-air-seeks-two-year-freeze-on-loan-repayment-express-reports.html

          
          
              Kingfisher Airlines Ltd. has sought
a two-year freeze on repayment of about 60 billion rupees ($1.29
billion) of debt, the Financial Express reported, without saying
where it got the information.  
 The airline has mandated SBI Capital Markets Ltd. to
restructure its finances, the newspaper said.  
